Jim Corey https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jim_Corey 0 James Warren Corey (October 19, 1883 – January 10, 1956) was an American actor. He appeared in 315 films between 1914 and 1948. He was born in Nebraska and died in Los Angeles, California. His grave is located at Valhalla Memorial Park Cemetery.
